comment: Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Gallinari's (DEN) arm that affects his layup attempt.
Booker (UTA) makes contact with the Faried's (DEN) arm, affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
LATR and R-SLA show that Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Faried (DEN) that affects his balance and ability to catch the alley-oop.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Faried (DEN) prior to going OOB was confirmed.
Faried (DEN) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact that does not affect Hayward's (UTA) RSBQ on the drive.
Faried (DEN) makes contact with Favors' (UTA) arm after he secures the rebound.
Faried (DEN) sets the screen on Hood (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Hayward (UTA) makes contact with Gallinari (DEN) that affects his RSBQ at the start of the drive.
Harris (DEN) commits a take foul during rebounding against Gobert (UTA).
Favors (UTA) makes incidental contact with Jokic (DEN) after he releases his shot attempt.
Harris (DEN) maintains legal guarding position and legally contests Hood's (UTA) shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) clamps Favors' (UTA) arm, affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Mudiay (DEN) and Favors (UTA) make incidental contact with one another while chasing after the loose ball.

After communicating with the Replay Center, there was conclusive video evidence that showed that Favors (UTA) was not OOB while making contact with the ball. The ruling on the court was overturned and Utah was awarded possession.
Harris (DEN) commits a take foul on Hayward (UTA).
